reviewText: I enjoyed watching this series.  I was glad they were able to give it a good ending.
Sad when it went off the air... now I can watch it whenever I want!
Loved the series when it was on TV. Now I can watch it any time I want to, and in sequence.
The season 3 dvds did not work, all of them in the case. I would like to get a new season 3. I would send these back if you would like.
Loved the series, wish it still was on
